headline: Citizens Financial Group Announces Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Earnings Conference Call Details
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., January 05, 2026--As previously announced, Citizens Financial Group, Inc. (NYSE: CFG) will report its fourth quarter and full year 2025 earnings on January 21, 2026. The news release and supplemental materials will be available at http://investor.citizensbank.com. CFG management will host a live conference call that morning with details as follows:
